name: Viggis Multicuisine Restaurant with Bistro

reviews.review_text: Ordered a lot of food and overall it was good. Atmosphere is nice. It was just some of the dishes did not have much tastes like the Mussels fry and crab fry (mostly seafood things) was also a little bland but the rest of the food like chicken crispy, lollipops, dragon chicken, crispy vegetables, etc were pretty good. Their noodles are also good. I would definitely recommend it. Reasonably priced and they offer delivery. Good restaurant to come too or order from.

Had gone to have King Fish thali with family. Enough car parking space. Service is good .Friendly staff, very prompt service. A good portion of king  fish is provided in the fish thali and reasonable price.
Food is really good. Love all their dishes: squids butter garlic, mutton biryani and thali are my regular dishes. Cannot get bored of them!

description:
### Viggis Multicuisine Restaurant with Bistro: A Culinary Haven in Tivim

Nestled in the charming town of Tivim, Viggis Multicuisine Restaurant with Bistro boasts an impressive rating of **4.2 stars**, with **942 reviews** attesting to its delightful offerings. Known for its diverse menu that emphasizes **thali** (27 mentions), **veg food** (21 mentions), and commendable **food quality** (17 mentions), Viggis stands out as a popular dining destination for both local food enthusiasts and travelers.

#### Ambiance & Design

Stepping into Viggis, guests are greeted by a welcoming atmosphere characterized by tasteful décor and ample natural light. The bistro-style setup invites patrons to relax while savoring their meals, making it an ideal spot for family gatherings or casual outings with friends. Photographic highlights, such as vibrant floral arrangements and cozy seating arrangements, create an inviting backdrop for the dining experience. Reviewers noted the overall ambiance as pleasant, with some enjoying the nice blend of background music that enhances the dining experience.

#### Menu & Culinary Experience

Viggis offers a rich culinary journey with its extensive menu featuring signature dishes that reflect a harmonious blend of flavors. Highlights include the **King Fish Thali**, known for its generous portions of perfectly cooked fish at a reasonable price—a top choice among families. Reviews frequently laud the **squid butter garlic**, **mutton biryani**, and various **vegetarian options**, showcasing that both meat lovers and vegetarians will find something to relish here. However, some diners have pointed out that certain seafood dishes, like the mussels fry and crab fry, could benefit from a touch more seasoning. Food is presented attractively, making each dish a feast for both the palate and the eyes. 

#### Customer Experience & Service

Viggis prides itself on its efficient and friendly service. Patrons consistently commend the staff for their promptness and willingness to assist, which significantly enhances the overall dining experience. Many customers have praised the ample **parking space**, making it convenient for families and groups. Whether dining in or opting for delivery, Viggis manages to cater to its customers effectively, ensuring a smooth experience from start to finish.

#### Popularity & Reviews

With a strong presence on social media, Viggis has garnered positive buzz, illustrating its popularity within the community. The consistent theme in reviews highlights the restaurant's value for money, excellent food quality, and welcoming service. It’s evident that many diners have cherished memories associated with their visits, often returning for their favorite dishes. While there may not be any specific critic awards mentioned, the high rating signals a reliable establishment that resonates well with its patrons.

#### Utilizing Visual Content

The charm of Viggis is beautifully captured in customer-provided photos that showcase both the food and the ambiance. Photos like the elegant display of the King Fish Thali and inviting interior designs provide a visual feast that complements the written review testimonials. These snapshots reflect the restaurant's vibrant atmosphere and the appetizing offerings that make it a popular choice for diners looking to indulge in a memorable meal.

### Conclusion

In essence, Viggis Multicuisine Restaurant with Bistro in Tivim emerges as a culinary gem that successfully marries quality food and exceptional service. With a menu that caters to various palates and a comforting atmosphere that encourages diners to linger a bit longer, it’s no surprise that this bistro continues to receive rave reviews. Whether you’re in the mood for a hearty **thali** or a savory **veg meal**, a visit to Viggis promises to be a fulfilling experience.
